title: War of the Roses: He Vacationed with Her Family Without Her
description: Scott's girlfriend, Avery, said she wanted to "stay home to study" while he went on vacation to Jamaica with HER family.  He's close with her family so it's not weird, but wants to know if she really stayed home for the reason she claims.  Find out if Avery was cheating on War of the Roses!
